    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1920-10-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1920-10-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="562"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d562">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/2995½</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The British Ambassador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Geddes</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-10-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 1, 1920</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 642</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Secretary</hi>: As you are no doubt aware, a
                    meeting of the China Consortium Banking Groups is to be held in New York in the
                    course of this month.</p>
                <pb facs="0673" n="575" xml:id="pg_575"/>
                <p>My Government have suggested to Sir C. S. Addis, the British Representative, that
                    he should discourage any official discussion of the wider political issues by
                    the Consortium Groups and they wish me to suggest to you the desirability of
                    making a similar recommendation to the Representative of the American Group.</p>
                <p>Believe me [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">A. C. Geddes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
